title: Welcome Back, Tracy Morgan
itunes:title: Welcome Back, Tracy Morgan
description:
THU 10/13 - The Breakfast Club welcomes Tracy Morgan back to the studio with open arms and thankful prayers after his tragic accident. The "30 Rock/SNL" star tells Envy, Angela & Charlamagne about his journey from recovery back to comedy and how he's turned his pain into laughter. Good to see you back at it, Mr. Morgan!
